DESCRIPTION:\nYou have been invited to a recurring meeting for FDC3 Sail\n\
 nFDC3-Sail is FINOS's open source implementation of the FDC3 interoperabil
 ity standard\, a browser based desktop agent that lets financial apps talk
  to each other through intent resolution\, channel linking and directory s
 earch.\nThis quarter our focus is moving Sail to v3\, and that will run th
 rough most of what we cover. Come along to raise issues\, help shape the r
 oadmap and share ideas so we get the most out of the project. Everyone wit
 h an interest in FDC3-Sail is welcome to join.\n\nWays to join meeting:\n\
 n1. Join from PC\, Mac\, iPad\, or Android\n\nhttps://zoom-lfx.platform.li
